Then she asks me if she can have 5 silver for the horse ride to Camelot.  Since I have a soft spot in my heart for Infiltrators, I gave her 30 silver, no big deal, right?<br>
Anyhow, she is generous in her praise of me, and insists on paying back my kindness.  Since 30 silver is really nothing by level 20 or so, I tell her to forget it, but she tells me that her alt has a staff, and she insists on giving it too me.<br>
I figure that I should take the staff, to keep from offending her.  I really don't need any staffs, I have 3 different staffs that con orange to me right now! (and I love them all)  But I didn't want to hurt her feelings by refusing.  So I sat down and waited.<br>
Pretty soon this truly ugly brute of an Armsman comes up and hands me a staff that cons purple to me!!!!  At level 34, I don't think that there are many con purple staffs out there anymore!<br>
This staff is +2 staff, +2 Enhance, +2 rejuv, and +2 Parry. +25% Bonus.   Absolutely amazing!  And I have it because I gave 30 silver to a newbie.<br>
-- Sometimes.....Good things happen at the most unexpected times. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6B8E23><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/urajivan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rajivan</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/misc_2.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#5F9EA0>(3/28/02 1:01:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1005.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GREAT CAESER'S GHOST!</span><hr size=1> Yes, I agree, good deeds do come back to those that perform them selfishly.<br>
